                            nostra, per inceptos himenaeos.
                        </p>
                    </section>

                    <section>
                        <h2
                            class="text-2xl font-bold text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 mb-4"
                        >
                            4. Cookies
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            Morbi accumsan ipsum velit. Nam nec tellus a odio
                            tincidunt auctor a ornare odio. Mauris in erat
                            justo. Nullam ac urna eu felis dapibus condimentum
